title: Cabinet bath with round window

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a cabinet bath with round window, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a front, elevational view of a cabinet bath with round window showing our new design;
FIG. 2 is a top view whereof;
FIG. 3 is left hand side, elevational view whereof, the right hand side a mirror image thereof;
FIG. 4 is a bottom view whereof; and
FIG. 5 is a rear, elevational view whereof; and,

FIGS. 6–8 are elevational views of another embodiment of a cabinet bath with round window showing our new design, with FIG. 6 from the front, FIG. 7 from the rear, and FIG. 8 from the left hand side with the right hand side a mirror image thereof. Bottom and rear views correspond analogously to those of FIGS. 4 and 5.
Features shown in broken lines form no part of our design.
